                    <span>This book is great and has helped me tremendously in being more confident in prospecting new business for my line of work.  It gives excellent advise on deal making - everything from the initial sales call to closing the deal.  It hits on points critical to strategic planning and developing a strong sales action plan.  An A+++ book!!</span>
                  
